'''Quenta Silmarillion''' can refer to:

*''[[The Silmarillion]]'', the book edited by [[Christopher Tolkien]], published in [[1977]].
**'''''[[Quenta Silmarillion]]''''': '''The History of the Silmarils''', third and main part of this book.

*''[[The Earliest 'Silmarillion']]'' or ''Sketch of the Mythology'', the second chapter of ''[[The Shaping of Middle-earth]]''.
*''[[The Quenta]]'' or ''Quenta Noldorinwa'', the third chapter of ''The Shaping of Middle-earth''.
*''[[Quenta Silmarillion (Lost Road)]]'', the ninth chapter of ''[[The Lost Road and Other Writings]]''.
*[[The Later Quenta Silmarillion|The Later ''Quenta Silmarillion'']], the third part of ''[[Morgoth's Ring]]''.
*The Later ''Quenta Silmarillion'', the second part of ''[[The War of the Jewels]]''.
